                </div>
                <div class="why-card">
                    <div class="why-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-people-group"></i></div>
                    <h3>Inclusive Culture</h3>
                    <p>We celebrate diversity and inclusion. Every voice is valued, every background is welcome and every team member is treated with respect and fairness.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="why-card">
                    <div class="why-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-laptop-code"></i></div>
                    <h3>Innovation Driven</h3>
                    <p>Be part of a bank that is at the forefront of financial technology. We encourage creative thinking, embrace new ideas and reward those who challenge the status quo.</p>
                </div>
